Features implemented:
1. Discover screen with chip-based search inputs (Location, Persona, Domain)
2. Event card grid with circular score gauges (color-coded: green/amber/red)
3. Sort controls (relevance score, date)
4. Detail drawer with three tabs (The Who, The How, The Where)
5. My Outreach pipeline with 4-column Kanban (Saved, Contacted, Responded, Partnered)
6. Pipeline persistence via localStorage
7. Sample data toggle
8. Copy-to-clipboard with inline confirmation
9. Draft Email via mailto: links
10. Agent activity monitoring via useLyzrAgentEvents
11. Loading skeletons and error states
12. Responsive layout
